(19, '2021-10-13 08:20:59', 'a:1:{i:0;s:15:\"admin@gmail.com\";}', '[Vay tiền online] Your Site is Experiencing a Technical Issue', 'Howdy!\r\n\r\nSince WordPress 5.2 there is a built-in feature that detects when a plugin or theme causes a fatal error on your site, and notifies you with this automated email.\r\n\nIn this case, WordPress caught an error with your theme, Finance.\n\r\nFirst, visit your website (http://localhost/vaytientietkiem/) and check for any visible issues. Next, visit the page where the error was caught (http://localhost/vaytientietkiem/vaytientietkiem/wp-admin/admin-ajax.php) and check for any visible issues.\r\n\r\nPlease contact your host for assistance with investigating this issue further.\r\n\r\nIf your site appears broken and you can\'t access your dashboard normally, WordPress now has a special \"recovery mode\". This lets you safely login to your dashboard and investigate further.\r\n\r\nhttp://localhost/vaytientietkiem/wp-login.php?action=enter_recovery_mode&rm_token=zv5COhh56xu1W2Gbqs3Bwp&rm_key=wHFoqlRjthGxILDiA8dw96\r\n\r\nTo keep your site safe, this link will expire in 1 day. Don\'t worry about that, though: a new link will be emailed to you if the error occurs again after it expires.\r\n\r\nWhen seeking help with this issue, you may be asked for some of the following information:\r\nWordPress version 5.8\r\nCurrent theme: Finance (version 1.1)\r\nCurrent plugin:  (version )\r\nPHP version 8.0.5\r\n\r\n\n\nError Details\n=============\nAn error of type E_PARSE was caused in line 738 of the file D:\\xampp\\htdocs\\vaytientietkiem\\wp-content\\themes\\finance\\functions.php. Error message: Unclosed \'{\' on line 721', 'a:0:{}', 'Invalid address:  (From): wordpress@localhost'),
(20, '2021-10-23 08:45:10', 'a:1:{i:0;s:15:\"admin@gmail.com\";}', '[Vay tiền online] Your Site is Experiencing a Technical Issue', 'Howdy!\r\n\r\nSince WordPress 5.2 there is a built-in feature that detects when a plugin or theme causes a fatal error on your site, and notifies you with this automated email.\r\n\nIn this case, WordPress caught an error with one of your plugins, Custom Permalinks.\n\r\nFirst, visit your website (http://localhost/vaytientietkiem/) and check for any visible issues. Next, visit the page where the error was caught (http://localhost/vaytientietkiem/vaytientietkiem/wp-admin/admin.php?page=cp-taxonomy-permalinks) and check for any visible issues.\r\n\r\nPlease contact your host for assistance with investigating this issue further.\r\n\r\nIf your site appears broken and you can\'t access your dashboard normally, WordPress now has a special \"recovery mode\". This lets you safely login to your dashboard and investigate further.\r\n\r\nhttp://localhost/vaytientietkiem/wp-login.php?action=enter_recovery_mode&rm_token=N3X8Tf7jjIjI4R8kwaNClF&rm_key=M1NrJEH5lIqEf83MExN8Xn\r\n\r\nTo keep your site safe, this link will expire in 1 day. Don\'t worry about that, though: a new link will be emailed to you if the error occurs again after it expires.\r\n\r\nWhen seeking help with this issue, you may be asked for some of the following information:\r\nWordPress version 5.8\r\nCurrent theme: Finance (version 1.1)\r\nCurrent plugin: Custom Permalinks (version 2.0.1)\r\nPHP version 8.0.5\r\n\r\n\n\nError Details\n=============\nAn error of type E_ERROR was caused in line 60 of the file D:\\xampp\\htdocs\\vaytientietkiem\\wp-content\\plugins\\custom-permalinks\\admin\\class-custom-permalinks-taxonomies.php. Error message: Uncaught TypeError: count(): Argument #1 ($var) must be of type Countable|array, bool given in D:\\xampp\\htdocs\\vaytientietkiem\\wp-content\\plugins\\custom-permalinks\\admin\\class-custom-permalinks-taxonomies.php:60\nStack trace:\n#0 D:\\xampp\\htdocs\\vaytientietkiem\\wp-content\\plugins\\custom-permalinks\\admin\\class-custom-permalinks-taxonomies-table.php(490): Custom_Permalinks_Taxonomies::total_permalinks()\n#1 D:\\xampp\\htdocs\\vaytientietkiem\\wp-content\\plugins\\custom-permalinks\\admin\\class-custom-permalinks-taxonomies-table.php(138): Custom_Permalinks_Taxonomies_Table->prepare_items()\n#2 D:\\xampp\\htdocs\\vaytientietkiem\\wp-content\\plugins\\custom-permalinks\\admin\\class-custom-permalinks-admin.php(140): Custom_Permalinks_Taxonomies_Table::output()\n#3 D:\\xampp\\htdocs\\vaytientietkiem\\wp-includes\\class-wp-hook.php(303): Custom_Permalinks_Admin->taxonomy_permalinks_page(\'\')\n#4 D:\\xampp\\htdocs\\vaytientietkiem\\wp-includes\\class-wp-hook.php(327): WP_Hook->apply_filters(\'\', Array)\n#5 D:\\xampp\\htdocs\\vaytientietkiem\\wp-includes\\plugin.php(470): WP_Hook->do_action(Array)\n#6 D:\\xampp\\htdocs\\vaytientietkiem\\wp-admin\\admin.php(259): do_action(\'custom-permalin...\')\n#7 {main}\n  thrown', 'a:0:{}', 'Invalid address:  (From): wordpress@localhost'),
